{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83e\udd6a Bread &amp; Butter: Team Up, Fight Back!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83c\udf5e Dual Heroes, One Fight</strong> \u2013 You\u2019re a fearless slice of bread, but you\u2019re never alone. Your butter companion battles by your side, upgradable and unstoppable, in this chaotic auto-combat survival fest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83e\udd55 Evil Veggie Onslaught</strong> \u2013 Face 25 waves of angry, evil vegetables\u2014broccoli brutes, tomato terrors, and more\u2014all out to squash you and your buttery buddy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83d\udd2b Auto-Fire Frenzy</strong> \u2013 Weapons blaze nonstop. You dodge, weave, and survive on a tight map swarming with foes\u2014run circles or blast through, your call.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Double the Upgrades</strong> \u2013 Kit out you and your butter with up to six weapons each, stacking six tiers of wild effects. Flaming toast? Dashing butter deathmachine? Build it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83d\udca5 Power-Up Chaos</strong> \u2013 Stack absurd items and buffs for ridiculous runs\u2014every combo\u2019s a new way to shred the veggie horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83c\udf7d\ufe0f Pick Your Pair</strong> \u2013 Mix and match Bread &amp; Butter duos, each with killer perks. Dash through foes, scoop loot, or brawl up close\u2014tons of teams to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83c\udfa8 Sassy Cartoon Carnage</strong> \u2013 Fast-paced action meets bold, cheeky characters\u2014grumpy carrots, smug celery, and bread with attitude.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83d\udd25 Survive the Madness</strong> \u2013 25 waves. Tiny map. Tons of enemies. Weak? Run for your life. Strong? Crush \u2018em all. Prove bread beats veggies every time.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3455040?t=174047331